msgid ""
"Calligra Sheets is a fully-featured calculation and spreadsheet tool. Use it "
"to quickly create and calculate various business-related spreadsheets, such "
"as income and expenditure, employee working hours, etc."
msgstr ""
"Calligra ListoviSheets je kompletno opremljen kalkulacijski i tabelarni "
"alat. Koristite ga da brzo kreirate i izračunati različite poslovne vezane "
"tabele, kao što su prihodi i rashodi, radno vrijeme, itd"

